dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures. "Entered according to act of Congress in the year 1833 by Illman & Pilbrow in the Clerk's office of the District Court for the Southern District of New-York." Prime meridians: Greenwich and Washington. Inset: Southern part of Florida. Original version published New-York: Illman & Pilbrow, [1833]; Scale approximately 1:9,000,000
